{"tid":1476323,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候學下用美金","createTime":"2019-08-15T18:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T01:31:43.000Z","uid":202262,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3648041a311960591b2f3323c6e270e050ce2ed1","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:51:05.000Z","msg":"見呢排咁多人持有美金 但普遍都係$100<br />\n不如我地今日<span style=\"color: red;\">認識</span>一下各式各樣嘅美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">硬幣與紙鈔的種類</span></span><br />\n基本單位為美元（dollar, $）跟美分(cent, &cent;)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AN3GkYh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAN3GkYh.jpg&h=a65f6478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有六種通用紙鈔面額，分別為1, 5, 10, 20, 50, 100元。<br />\n硬幣有六種幣值，分別為1, 5, 10, 25, 50 美分 和 1 美元。<br />\n不過50美分與1美元硬幣較為罕見。 <br />\n1 &cent; (Penny) 5 &cent; (Nickel) 10 &cent; (Dime) 25 &cent; (quarter)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357bebb4021b2d737198291dd7dec77ad77a18d0","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:51:59.000Z","msg":"O! say can you see, by the dawn's early light,"},{"pid":"169baa0cb96e2a239dc2d4dcb403092396097159","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:52:09.000Z","msg":"What so proudly we hailed at the twilight's last gleaming,"},{"pid":"26b6c6e3c0584d8f1c82b01347a319c7ae1b2f19","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:52:19.000Z","msg":"Whose broad stripes and bright stars through the perilous fight,"},{"pid":"1e7ad465a26fc5f58424a59b9b841d592076cddf","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:52:31.000Z","msg":"O'er the ramparts we watched, were so gallantly streaming?"},{"pid":"661b624fe8b612b37e73bcf70be7811637aa9e2c","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:52:41.000Z","msg":"And the rockets' red glare, the bombs bursting in air,"},{"pid":"9153dc01a51c814c7f572d904194d3037892fc09","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:52:53.000Z","msg":"Gave proof through the night that our flag was still there;"},{"pid":"3b0f6d540b28e22348db11fd2ffe90b1fbc38cd3","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:53:03.000Z","msg":"O! say does that star-spangled banner yet wave"},{"pid":"5716fc2baa45c250cccc3393825d9a4782ba5220","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:53:13.000Z","msg":"O'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?"},{"pid":"bfdf9a12173b72af9053876e204bd6e901b48660","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:53:35.000Z","msg":"On the shore dimly seen through the mists of the deep,"},{"pid":"a5cc7c677f5d24b95965368742d0c8ab258a4d06","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:53:46.000Z","msg":"Where the foe's haughty host in dread silence reposes,"},{"pid":"d88148ecef8a133480b3f9da531d2cfb66d846ad","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:53:56.000Z","msg":"What is that which the breeze, o'er the towering steep,"},{"pid":"524a0ed39e4ee9d166f5a7e0fc66b5be8e764ed3","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:54:06.000Z","msg":"As it fitfully blows, half conceals, half discloses?"},{"pid":"2b626cfdfd96bf5a847036417bd4fe36053acd16","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:54:16.000Z","msg":"Now it catches the gleam of the morning's first beam,"},{"pid":"85f04581dc8d4af39993f609b963b62401ca6c7c","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:54:26.000Z","msg":"In full glory reflected now shines in the stream:"},{"pid":"9c14ce03459e1e63facaae2fe583e617e1cba520","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:54:44.000Z","msg":"'Tis the star-spangled banner, O! long may it wave"},{"pid":"3aee5dbfa02fe5c4f0bbb6d8258e012d336c6940","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:54:54.000Z","msg":"O'er the land of the free and the home of the brave."},{"pid":"360d207b6e888bf354ca3209048611e3613fc0fc","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:55:39.000Z","msg":"And where is that band who so vauntingly swore"},{"pid":"78f5e5db0ad3ada70223324bfce22f41e50a79b8","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:55:49.000Z","msg":"That the havoc of war and the battle's confusion,"},{"pid":"5f53d0e6a60a565337371450563edef3b8d8f0b2","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:56:04.000Z","msg":"A home and a country, should leave us no more?"},{"pid":"752df25fbc593a68b368fbbcf21833fe107c8651","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:56:16.000Z","msg":"Their blood has washed out their foul footsteps' pollution."},{"pid":"a3705721b504296e93bc5f2d3013d838b75f9ea8","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:56:26.000Z","msg":"No refuge could save the hireling and slave"},{"pid":"c5e0a51b6b6b3de79c07be7c87ef7f35fd83a085","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:56:36.000Z","msg":"From the terror of flight, or the gloom of the grave:"},{"pid":"b0d03fff7bde8894b4e8ec18db8e0e9cd818feb9","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:56:47.000Z","msg":"And the star-spangled banner in triumph doth wave,"},{"pid":"ab3e130d897c971dca1f65ed2af67ef4e50d669c","tid":1476323,"uid":202262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:56:58.000Z","msg":"O'er the land of the free and the home of the brave."}]}